Package: xrender1
Version: 0.8.4
Revision: 1
BuildDepends: render1-dev (>= 0.8-1), x11-dev
Depends: %N-shlibs
Source: http://freedesktop.org/~xlibs/release/libXrender-%v.tar.bz2
Source-MD5: c745339dbe5f05cff8950b71a739e34c
ConfigureParams: --prefix=%p/lib/%N --sysconfdir=/private/etc --bindir=%p/bin --mandir=%p/share/man
CompileScript: <<
#!/bin/sh

  export PKG_CONFIG_PATH=%p/lib/render1/lib/pkgconfig
  ./configure %c
  make
<<
InstallScript: <<
 make -j1 install DESTDIR=%d
 install -d -m 755 %i/share/doc/%n
<<
SplitOff: <<
  Package: %N-shlibs
  Files: lib/%N/lib/libXrender.*.dylib
  Shlibs: %p/lib/%N/lib/libXrender.1.dylib 4.0.0 (%n >= 0.8.4-1)
  Description: Shared libraries for libXrender
<<
DocFiles: AUTHORS COPYING ChangeLog INSTALL NEWS README
License: OSI-Approved
Description: Libraries and development headers for the X render extension
Maintainer: Benjamin Reed <ranger@befunk.com>
Homepage: http://freedesktop.org/~xlibs/
DescPackaging: <<
This package should not be linked against unless absolutely
necessary.  If you must link against it, you need to set
some variables.

  CPPFLAGS:        add -I%p/lib/%N/include
  CFLAGS:          you might need the same as CPPFLAGS
  PKG_CONFIG_PATH: add %p/lib/%N/lib/pkgconfig
<<
